7 minutes ago, dino1984 said:

Game crashes at start up every time I start it. I have never had similar issues, but I played last time like 6 months ago.

 

So it's updated since you last played?

5 minutes ago, Daveroski said:

So it's updated since you last played?

I guess Steam is auto updating it every time there is any update...

 

CKAN is saying 1.3.1.1891

Edited December 30, 2017 by dino1984

Then there is a good chance that one or more of your mods is no longer compatible.

Most of us copy the Game Directory to another place on the Hard drive and play it from there then when steam updates, it will not be updating the copy that we are playing.
